 Review comment:
   Since children is not referenced outside of the loop, I'd do
   
   ```
   for (const auto& child_fn: result.ValueOrDie())
   ```
   
   I also tend to avoid `result` naming and use `maybe_x` instead, e.g. `maybe_children`. Helps to understand when typed with auto.

